snippet.textDisplay: Haven't seen most of these but Hellboy was the worst Triple A movie I've seen in a long while. The editing was terrible, acting was terrible, writing and plot was a fucking dumpster fire. I can sit through most movies. I've seen Dragonball Evolution twice, I've seen BloodRayne twice, but I fell asleep 30 minutes into this movie, woke up the next moring to try and finish it, got about 10 more minutes in and just turned it off and never felt the desire to see how it ends. If I can sit through Dragonball Evolution but can't sit through Hellboy, then that movie is fucking terrible.
